Package no.ntnu.imt3281.project1 Description

This package is meant to simplify the usage of GridBagLayout. Instead of manually typing in all the values, this package allows you to set up objects in a graphical user interface. All classes extend BaseComponent, which implements the Serializable interface.
Author:
sadario, thomasgg
